Package arduino.arduinocom

This package contains all of the classes necessary to communicate with an Arduino in a fingerprint robot.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Arduino
    This class represents an Arduino.
    ArduinoCom
    This class represents a connection to an Arduino.
    ExecutionStatus
    An object used to monitor the status of the execution of a command on the Arduino.
    NetworkArduinoCom
    This class represents a connection to an Arduino over Ethernet.
    SerialArduinoCom
    This class represents a connection to an Arduino over USB.
    SerialInputStream
    This is an input stream for serial devices.
    SerialOutputStream
    A output stream for sending data through a serial port.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    STATE
    Represents the states that an execution could be in.
